title: Perth Wildcats come from behind to defeat Illawarra Hawks (Perth Wildcats Pty Ltd)
text: ( Source : Perth Wildcats Pty Ltd ) The Perth Wildcats have come from behind to claim a 106-99 victory in a thrilling contest against the Illawarra Hawks . Outscoring the Hawks 29-17 in the final quarter, the shorthanded Wildcats played tough,
